/span>]); <span class=\"keyword\">echo</span> <span class=\"string\">\"&lt;/pre&gt;\"</span>; <span class=\"keyword\">die</span>();&#125;<span class=\"meta\">?&gt;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p>\n","comments":true,"excerpt":"注意：本文分享给安全从业人员、网站开发人员以及运维人员在日常工作防范恶意攻击,请勿恶意使用下面介绍技术进行非法攻击操作。。[TOC]","categories":[{"name":"Backdoor","path":"api/categories/Backdoor.json"}],"tags":[{"name":"脚本后门","path":"api/tags/脚本后门.json"}]}